All right, I'm coming.

16
00:07:49,344 --> 00:07:52,264
For God's sake.

17
00:07:57,769 --> 00:08:01,022
Yes?

18
00:08:03,233 --> 00:08:06,653
What do you want?

19
00:08:08,071 --> 00:08:13,285
