March.

208
00:32:04,841 --> 00:32:08,970
Face right.
March.

209
00:32:13,725 --> 00:32:18,772
Face right. March!

210
00:32:19,022 --> 00:32:21,233
March!

211
00:32:32,869 --> 00:32:36,623
That's enough. Stop.

212
00:32:42,295 --> 00:32:45,882
Stop it!

213
00:33:08,947 --> 00:33:15,036
Boy, be careful. You play with fire.

214
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:29,551
Okay,
I can tell you're not into this.

215
00:33:29,718 --> 00:33:34,055
No, I am. Really.
It just takes me a while.

216
00:33:34,931 --> 00:33:40,145
I like you. You're the only guy
who never tried to impress me.

217
00:33:43,940 --> 00:33:49,154
- Can I ask you something?
- Sure.

218
00:33:50,739 --> 00:33:55,702
Do you ever wonder
why people do the things they do?

219
00:33:55,952 --> 00:34:01,249
Think about it. Seriously.

220
00:34:08,799 --> 00:34:13,762
It's better not to think.
It's better to just do it.

221
00:34:36,159 --> 00:34:40,205
Who are you, kitty?

222
00:34:49,714 --> 00:34:54,052
It's getting cold out here, kitty.

223
00:35:11,653 --> 00:35:15,574
- I'm sorry.
- We can try again later.

224
00:35:15,782 --> 00:35:22,205
- That's never happened before.
- It's all right.

225
00:35:23,874 --> 00:35:28,503
Could you blow that
the other way, please.

226
00:35:31,548 --> 00:35:36,887
- Maybe you just don't like me.
- No, it's not that at all.

227
00:35:37,053 --> 00:35:42,684
- I really do.
- Maybe you just don't like girls.

228
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:12,047
Kitty ...

229
00:36:12,756 --> 00:36:15,425
Goodbye.

230
00:36:25,227 --> 00:36:28,730
You motherfucker!

231
00:37:02,931 --> 00:37:07,894
You have five more minutes.

232
00:37:37,507 --> 00:37:39,634
"Dear Mr. & Mrs. Bowden."

233
00:37:39,843 --> 00:37:44,598
"l suggest we have a conference
about Todd's first-semester grades."

234
00:37:44,765 --> 00:37:48,977
"ln light of his previous
outstanding work, -

235
00:37:49,144 --> 00:37:54,357
- it suggests a problem which
